OL,3,CIncrease in violent attacks against
OL,4,Ctransport workers in London, say union
OL,6,FUrgent action is needed to protect
OL,7,Ftransport workers in London amid an
OL,8,Fincrease in violent attacks and
OL,9,Faggression, according to a union.
OL,11,FThe Rail, Maritime and Transport union
OL,12,F(RMT) said its analysis of official
OL,13,Ffigures showed a 9% increase in
OL,14,Fincidents of violence against staff
OL,15,Facross London Underground, London
OL,16,FOverground, the Elizabeth Line and the
OL,17,FDocklands Light Railway in the year to
OL,18,FNovember 2025 compared with the
OL,19,Fprevious year.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
