OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773609114
OL,3,CIncrease in violent attacks against
OL,4,Ctransport workers in London, say union
OL,6,FThe union said its own study found
OL,7,Fthat nearly two-thirds of staff
OL,8,Fexperienced workplace violence in the
OL,9,Fpast year, rising to 85% among London
OL,10,FUnderground station and revenue
OL,11,Fprotection staff.
OL,13,FAround half of those incidents
OL,14,Foccurred while staff were lone
OL,15,Fworking, said the RMT.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
