CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773609114
OL,3,CIncrease in violent attacks against
OL,4,Ctransport workers in London, say union
OL,6,FRMT general secretary Eddie Dempsey
OL,7,Fsaid: "Violence and abuse against
OL,8,Ftransport workers is a serious and
OL,9,Fgrowing problem on London's public
OL,10,Ftransport network and our members are
OL,11,Freporting that incidents are becoming
OL,12,Fmore frequent.
OL,14,F"It is completely unacceptable for our
OL,15,Fmembers to have to face such an
OL,16,Fintolerable situation.
OL,26,@oD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
