PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773609114
OL,3,CIncrease in violent attacks against
OL,4,Ctransport workers in London, say union
OL,6,F"Increasing staffing levels across the
OL,7,Fnetwork, ending lone working,
OL,8,Fproviding safe places of refuge and an
OL,9,Fincreased British Transport Police
OL,10,Fpresence are key to tackling the risk
OL,11,Fof violence.
OL,13,F"Transport workers keep London moving
OL,14,Fand they deserve to be able to do
OL,15,Ftheir jobs without fear of abuse or
OL,16,Fassault."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
