CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773609114
OL,3,CIncrease in violent attacks against
OL,4,Ctransport workers in London, say union
OL,6,FOn Thursday 12 March, the mayor and
OL,7,FTransport for London (TfL) brought
OL,8,Ftogether senior transport leaders, the
OL,9,Fpolice and trade union representatives
OL,10,Ffor a summit on work-related violence
OL,11,Fand aggression, aimed at reducing
OL,12,Fviolence, abuse and intimidation
OL,13,Fagainst transport staff, including its
OL,14,Foperators and contractors.
OL,16,FTransport for London commissioner Andy
OL,17,FLord said: "Every member of our
OL,18,Fworkforce deserves to feel safe,
OL,19,Frespected and supported as they carry
OL,20,Fout the essential job of keeping
OL,21,FLondon moving.
OL,26,@yD@LOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773609114
OL,3,CIncrease in violent attacks against
OL,4,Ctransport workers in London, say union
OL,6,F"While we've made real progress in
OL,7,Freducing the most harmful forms of
OL,8,Fviolence and aggression, the rising
OL,9,Flevels of hostility and hate across
OL,10,Fsociety make it clear that we cannot
OL,11,Fbe complacent.
OL,13,F"Today's summit is about strengthening
OL,14,Four shared determination, across TfL,
OL,15,Four trade unions and the police, to
OL,16,Fbuild on the improvements we have
OL,17,Fachieved and to focus relentlessly on
OL,18,Fsafety and protection for our people."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@fO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
