OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773609114
OL,3,CIncrease in violent attacks against
OL,4,Ctransport workers in London, say union
OL,6,FMayor of London Sir Sadiq Khan said:
OL,7,F"Violence and aggression towards
OL,8,Fanyone at work is completely
OL,9,Funacceptable, and we must have zero
OL,10,Ftolerance for this on London's
OL,11,Ftransport network.
OL,13,F"Everyone has the right to work
OL,14,Fwithout fear of being assaulted,
OL,15,Fabused or threatened, and I'm
OL,16,Fdetermined to stamp out these harmful
OL,17,Fand traumatic incidents.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
