FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1773609114
OL,3,CIncrease in violent attacks against
OL,4,Ctransport workers in London, say union
OL,6,F"Today's summit reaffirms our
OL,7,Fcommitment to eliminating work-related
OL,8,Fviolence and aggression, while setting
OL,9,Fout further decisive action to protect
OL,10,Fall those who do vital work every day
OL,11,Fto keep the capital moving, as we
OL,12,Fcontinue building a safer London for
OL,13,Feveryone."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@JO]
